Codehesion enjoyed excellent growth over the past year and has strengthened its Android and iOS app development teams to cope with demand. The company is well-known for producing world-class mobile apps for the South African business market. Over the past year, Codehesion has helped many companies to develop and launch new Android and iPhone applications. Its latest projects include: Codehesion’s strong focus on producing quality mobile apps, and its excellent customer service, has made it the software developer of choice for many companies. This rapidly-growing demand has also helped Codehesion to add many experienced computer science and engineering graduates to its team. Codehesion CEO Hector Beyers said their success is thanks to their business strategy of focusing solely on delivering world-class Android and iOS apps and online portals. This strategy has enabled Codehsion to build highly-specialised skills and processes which help it to build websites and mobile apps fasters and more affordably than its competitors. “To date we have had a 100% success rate with our website and mobile app projects, which shows that our processes work well,” said Beyers. This article was published in partnership with Codehesion.